== Ṣṣbiṭaṛat d timrsal n tdusi ==
Iṭṭaf wammas asgnaf amsdaw Ibn Sina mraw id ṣṣbiṭaṛ d timrsal n usujji d tdusi d ussgnf, ad tnt igan d:

* Asgnaf Ibn Sina
* Asgnaf amẓlay
* Asgnaf n tazzanin
* Asinag anamur n tankulujit
* Asgnaf n trbayt n Swisi
* Ammas n tdusi n tarwa
* Asgnaf Mulay Yusf
* Ammas n uzzray d usmkl n uxsan
* Asgnaf Lɛiyyaci
* Asgnaf Rrazi

== Taẓẓiḍṛa ==
Ammas asgnaf amsdaw Ibn Sina ad igan CHU nna akkʷ imqqurn ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], s yat tẓẓiḍṛa n 2 347 tisiyin, d 328 730 izzrayn isnajyanin, 30 054 [[Aflay|uflay]] d  25 379 irwn ar gis zzrayn kra iga t usggʷas<ref>[http://www.churabat.ma/index.php/2013-01-31-06-37-23 Présentation] du CHU Ibn Sina</ref>

